---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import PageBanner from "../components/PageBanner.astro";
---

<Layout title="Get involved">
  <PageBanner slot="banner" title="Volunteering" />

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-6 auto-rows-auto md:auto-rows-[280px]"
    >
      <div
        class="md:col-span-5 md:row-span-2 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-weegee-teal bg-weegee-teal p-2 group cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 relative"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/pens.webp"
          alt="Coloured pens and art materials"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-7 md:row-span-2 bg-weegee-white rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-weegee-teal flex flex-col justify-center gap-4"
      >
        <h2
          class="text-3xl text-weegee-teal font-serif border-b pb-2 border-weegee-teal/10"
        >
          Join us!
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          We can't do what we do without you. We need you to join us: whether
          it's for an hour, an event or a weekend, you will help make a huge
          difference to us and the people that we welcome.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          Volunteering roles available can change week to week, depending on the
          need and availability. For the most up to date list or more
          information, the best first step is to email us at
          <a
            href="mailto:volunteering@refuweegee.co.uk"
            class="text-weegee-teal underline font-bold"
          >
            volunteering@refuweegee.co.uk
          </a>.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm italic text-weegee-black/70">
          We regularly run events at George Square—an excellent way to get
          familiar with our space! We encourage everyone to use our space before
          volunteering in it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-8 md:row-span-1 bg-weegee-yellow rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-weegee-yellow flex flex-col justify-center"
      >
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-weegee-black font-serif mb-2">
          Volunteer social
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          Every 6 weeks we get together to celebrate all things volunteering!
          It's a great mix of new volunteers, long serving volunteers and people
          who have never volunteered but want to know more! To find out the date
          of our next social just follow the link to our Events page.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-1 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-weegee-teal bg-weegee-teal p-2 group cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 relative"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/group.webp"
          alt="Volunteers grouping together"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-4 md:row-span-2 rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-weegee-teal bg-weegee-teal p-2 group cursor-pointer transition-transform duration-500 hover:-translate-y-1 relative"
      >
        <img
          src="/assets/drawing.webp"
          alt="Artistic welcoming drawing"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-2xl"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <div
        class="md:col-span-8 md:row-span-2 bg-weegee-white rounded-3xl p-8 border-2 border-weegee-teal flex flex-col justify-center gap-4"
      >
        <h2
          class="text-2xl text-weegee-black font-serif border-b pb-2 border-weegee-teal/10"
        >
          Corporate volunteering
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          We are constantly blown away by the positive impact teams of corporate
          volunteers can make in just one day. We love seeing groups come
          together to make a difference and regularly host teams of up to 12
          people, who dedicate their hours to helping us run core services.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base leading-relaxed">
          Whether it is sorting clothing donations, assisting customers in our
          free shop or simply making someone a cuppa and giving them a chance to
          practice their English - there are roles suited to everyone!
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-weegee-teal">
          If your team would like to support us, get in touch with Lily, our
          Corporate Relations Coordinator, at volunteering@refuweegee.co.uk
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
